summary: Natalie Dormer Splits With Boyfriend Of 11 Years – Right After Finally Making A Movie Together! – Perez Hilton
title: Natalie Dormer Splits With Boyfriend Of 11 Years – Right After Finally Making A Movie Together! – Perez Hilton
body:
No Purple Wedding IRL for Natalie Dormer! Which we guess is a good thing for Anthony Byrne…

The Game of Thrones actress confirmed to The New Statesman she and her director boyfriend have split after eleven years together.

While she didn’t go into the details, plenty of red flags were sent up during this Summer’s promotional tour for the film they cowrote, In Darkness.

She said she “wouldn’t recommend” writing with your significant other, he revealed it caused “massive arguments.”

We’ve heard not to poop where you eat, we guess the reverse is just as true?

In any case, they are in good company — see the many, many celeb splits from this year (below):

summary: We can’t keep calm! Masaba to officially bring 'Winter' in India
title: We can’t keep calm! Masaba to officially bring 'Winter' in India
body:
We can’t keep calm! Masaba to officially bring ‘Winter’ in India

As the year is coming to an end, the excitement is getting a bit higher as ace designer Masaba Gupta bags the official license to create ‘Game of Thrones’ merchandise.

Just like a reminder, Masaba shared the news again on her official Instagram handle and captioned the collab picture as, “Can I please say it one more time so it can hit me that I have a game of thrones collaboration next year.…
